<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.1">
<l>kalaṅka munnīr kaṭainta mutaṅ koṇṭimaiyōr</l>
<l>tuḷaṅkal tīra nalku cōtic cuṭarāya</l>
<l>valaṅkai yāḻi yiṭaṅkaic caṅka muṭaiyāṉūr</l>
<l>nalaṅkoḷ vāymai yantaṇar vāḻum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of him who has the conch in [his] left hand [and] in [his] right hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">the disc which is [like] the brilliant sun,</l>
<l>Who bestowed grace to end the anxiety of the unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l>Having brought [forth] ambrosia, churning the three-watered [sea]</l>
<l rend="indent">so it roiled,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where dwell priests of the virtuous truth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
